"{\"uid\": \"lancashiretelegraph.co.uk-news-24535656.skills-olympics-clitheroes-isabelle-baron-compete\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ConstructionEducationClitheroe  A highly skilled Clitheroe professional, who is Europe's leading competitor in her\\u00a0field,\\u00a0is heading to Lyon for the WorldSkills Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 49, \"end\": 58, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clitheroe\", \"score\": 0.9999993998405425, \"rank\": 6.001550313078121e-07, \"text\": \"Clitheroe\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clitheroe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clitheroe\"}, {\"begin\": 136, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"score\": 0.9999965059189088, \"rank\": 3.4938602617370727e-06, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\"}, {\"begin\": 149, \"end\": 160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldSkills\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WorldSkills\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldSkills\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldSkills\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Isabelle Barron, ranked as\\u00a0Europe's number one in\\u00a0the digital construction competition,\\u00a0won the gold medal at last year's European finals in Gdansk,\\u00a0Poland.\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 172, \"end\": 180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feral_child\", \"score\": 0.9967112764444476, \"rank\": 0.0032994222871183484, \"text\": \"Isabelle\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feral_child\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feral_child\"}, {\"begin\": 181, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999844312698, \"rank\": 1.5568285157893975e-08, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 313, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gda\\u0144sk\", \"score\": 0.999930269892225, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gdansk\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gda\\u0144sk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gda\\u0144sk\"}, {\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.9916433792199728, \"rank\": 0.005167812841469282, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Split into several tasks over the four days judges will mark competitors based on speed and accuracy.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Through practicing repeatedly on the software and reaching out to mentors, training managers, past competitors or people at work she has become adept and prepared for the competition.\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Isabelle\\u00a0said: \\\"I am so delighted to have the chance to go to the World Finals and face the ultimate test.\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Competition has helped me immeasurably in so many ways.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I tend to be quite an anxious person, but the intensity of focusing on competing, in public, and at such an elite level seems to have really helped me.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has allowed me to develop my personal skills as well as my confidence in myself and my ability and also to broaden my network.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, I won a gold at Euro skills in Gdansk, but now I am going to find out how good I am against the very best in the World.\\\"\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gda\\u0144sk\", \"score\": 0.999930269892225, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gdansk\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gda\\u0144sk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gda\\u0144sk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old gained a first-class degree in architectural technology at Sheffield Hallam University and now works for professional services consulting firm WSP, handling majorbusinessprojects.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1271, \"end\": 1287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield_Hallam_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.969290401026914e-22, \"text\": \"Sheffield Hallam\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield_Hallam_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sheffield_Hallam_University\"}, {\"begin\": 1355, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WSP_USA\", \"score\": 0.9951493713216759, \"rank\": 0.004874271632372265, \"text\": \"WSP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WSP_USA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WSP_USA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was while\\u00a0she was studying that she heard about the competition through one of her lecturers who suggested she should take part.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But winning is not\\u00a0the main objective for Isabelle who is focused on enjoying the environment and scale of the competition while\\u00a0also connecting with like-minded people.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"I do not think I am prepared for the scale of the competition and what it will be like, it will just be immense.\\\"\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This year marks the 47th WorldSkills Olympics, which is a global movement bringing together young professionals from across the world through competition-based training, assessment and benchmarking.\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Members of national teams test their abilities to achieve world-class standards with insights gained enabling the movement to embed world-class training standards across the UK.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.393798246215749e-11, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kicking off on September 10, there is expected to be 250,000 spectators with a glittering opening and closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be attended by President Macron and dozens of ministers of state and ambassadors.\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2347, \"end\": 2363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"President Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skills Minister Jacqui Smith said: \\\"I want to congratulate these talented young people who have been chosen to represent Team UK and show off the world-beating skills of our students and apprentices.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2431, \"end\": 2443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacqui_Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jacqui Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacqui_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacqui_Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 2541, \"end\": 2543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.393798246215749e-11, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To represent your country is an honour and a privilege, but also a reflection of the hard work and dedication you have all shown.\\\"\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There will be around 1,500 competitors at the week-long gathering in France where competitors will compete in more than 60 disciplines including cyber security, hairdressing, joinery and robotics and will be judged by the World's leading experts.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2818, \"end\": 2824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9896644515723759, \"rank\": 0.010364995869852822, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"WorldSkills UK, a government-funded charity, in partnership with Pearson has selected, trained and prepared the team during an exhausted period of regional and national competitions.\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3009, \"end\": 3011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.393798246215749e-11, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3062, \"end\": 3069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pearson_plc\", \"score\": 0.9644437647176252, 